ill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a190b1fc6760cfcfe3b1a8cdad670bce3bcff7","tid":1679090,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD53yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=62614062\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD53yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=f689bc1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD53yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=69202801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"cf152e09c0481e6810f258249131e2d53a5b4480","tid":1679090,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:29:31.000Z","msg":"如果係藍抵撚你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d9d3c4b9b6b0f70709f2f204703d564767d9de","tid":1679090,"uid":41744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"呢位藍屍鋪主係咪戇鳩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察係保護你先射彈<br />\n咁多暴徒係你鋪頭門口 擔心你會被裝修咋<br />\n良心當狗肺 25仔"},{"pid":"35df34fb71c17ed687016b42e8a16b03d045be04","tid":1679090,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:30:05.000Z","msg":"藍加藍變黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5329c0b26f9eb2c3c31074a4c5552740bb286cd2","tid":1679090,"uid":3297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人開名，好驚幫襯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7497a8b01ca659829e3f1a56d9bf3ca6cb3b33ef","tid":1679090,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf71a1cfc058e6bdf55e2cd667a172953a50e71","tid":1679090,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:26:3